      "author": "benjamonnguyen",
      "description": "### Link Feature\r\n`src:` language line option ([#18](https://github.com/benjamonnguyen/obsidian-todotxt-codeblocks/issues/18))\r\n- Link a *.txt file to the todotxt codeblock\r\n- Syntax: `src:<path/to/*.txt>`\r\n- Usage example: \\`\\`\\`todotxt src:todotxt/todo.txt\r\n<img width=\"568\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/benjamonnguyen/obsidian-todotxt-codeblocks/assets/43457281/05fe547f-678e-4ac0-8797-a91313198769\">\r\n\r\n### Breaking Changes\r\n- Changed archive.todotxt extension to archive.txt; please copy and paste archived tasks over to archive.txt.\r\n- Removed undo command because it was poorly implemented and incompatible with new link feature\r\n\r\n### Other Changes\r\n- fix: toggleCheckbox sort bug.\r\n- feature: `New codeblock at cursor` command",
