      "author": "benjamonnguyen",
      "description": "# Features\r\n- **Sorting** (listed in order of priority)\r\n  - `proj` (project)\r\n  - `ctx` (context)\r\n  - `status`\r\n  - `prio` (priority)\r\n  - `completed` (completed date)\r\n  - `due` (due date extension)\r\n  - `created` (created date)\r\n  - `default` (equivalent to \"sort:status sort:prio sort:completed sort:due sort:created\")\r\n- **Extensions**\r\n  - `due:` (Due date)\r\n  - `rec:` (Recurrence frequency)\r\n- **UI**\r\n  - Collapsible project groups\r\n  - Edit, add, and delete tasks in Live Preview\r\n  - Render Markdown links\r\n- **Archive** completed tasks to `archive.todotxt` file\r\n  - **Auto-archive** setting\r\n- **Autocompletion** for projects and contexts\r\n- **Commands**\r\n  - Create new task in focused list\r\n  - Undo user action",
